This Power BI dashboard provides a clear and interactive view of employee attrition within a company. It helps in understanding the reasons behind why employees leave, by analyzing different factors such as salary, age, gender, education level, and years spent in the organization. The report also includes key performance indicators like job role, department, and work experience to give a complete picture. With easy filters and visuals, it allows HR professionals and management to explore trends, compare different scenarios, and take data-driven steps to improve employee retention.
